{"snp4.10:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 4.10 ","snp4.10:0.2":"Purabhedasutta ","snp4.10:1.1":"“Kathamdassi kathamsilo, ","snp4.10:1.2":"upasantoti vuccati; ","snp4.10:1.3":"Tam me gotama pabruhi, ","snp4.10:1.4":"pucchito uttamam naram”. ","snp4.10:2.1":"“Vitatanho pura bheda, ","snp4.10:2.2":"(iti bhagava) ","snp4.10:2.3":"Pubbamantamanissito; ","snp4.10:2.4":"Vemajjhe nupasankheyyo, ","snp4.10:2.5":"Tassa natthi purakkhatam. ","snp4.10:3.1":"Akkodhano asantasi, ","snp4.10:3.2":"avikatthi akukkuco; ","snp4.10:3.3":"Mantabhani anuddhato, ","snp4.10:3.4":"sa ve vacayato muni. ","snp4.10:4.1":"Nirasatti anagate, ","snp4.10:4.2":"atitam nanusocati; ","snp4.10:4.3":"Vivekadassi phassesu, ","snp4.10:4.4":"ditthisu ca na niyati. ","snp4.10:5.1":"Patilino akuhako, ","snp4.10:5.2":"apihalu amacchari; ","snp4.10:5.3":"Appagabbho ajeguccho, ","snp4.10:5.4":"pesuneyye ca no yuto. ","snp4.10:6.1":"Satiyesu anassavi, ","snp4.10:6.2":"atimane ca no yuto; ","snp4.10:6.3":"Sanho ca patibhanava, ","snp4.10:6.4":"na saddho na virajjati. ","snp4.10:7.1":"Labhakamya na sikkhati, ","snp4.10:7.2":"alabhe ca na kuppati; ","snp4.10:7.3":"Aviruddho ca tanhaya, ","snp4.10:7.4":"rasesu nanugijjhati. ","snp4.10:8.1":"Upekkhako sada sato, ","snp4.10:8.2":"na loke mannate samam; ","snp4.10:8.3":"Na visesi na niceyyo, ","snp4.10:8.4":"tassa no santi ussada. ","snp4.10:9.1":"Yassa nissayana natthi, ","snp4.10:9.2":"natva dhammam anissito; ","snp4.10:9.3":"Bhavaya vibhavaya va, ","snp4.10:9.4":"tanha yassa na vijjati. ","snp4.10:10.1":"Tam brumi upasantoti, ","snp4.10:10.2":"Kamesu anapekkhinam; ","snp4.10:10.3":"Gantha tassa na vijjanti, ","snp4.10:10.4":"Atari so visattikam. ","snp4.10:11.1":"Na tassa putta pasavo, ","snp4.10:11.2":"Khettam vatthunca vijjati; ","snp4.10:11.3":"Atta vapi niratta va, ","snp4.10:11.4":"Na tasmim upalabbhati. ","snp4.10:12.1":"Yena nam vajjum puthujjana, ","snp4.10:12.2":"Atho samanabrahmana; ","snp4.10:12.3":"Tam tassa apurakkhatam, ","snp4.10:12.4":"Tasma vadesu nejati. ","snp4.10:13.1":"Vitagedho amacchari, ","snp4.10:13.2":"Na ussesu vadate muni; ","snp4.10:13.3":"Na samesu na omesu, ","snp4.10:13.4":"Kappam neti akappiyo. ","snp4.10:14.1":"Yassa loke sakam natthi, ","snp4.10:14.2":"Asata ca na socati; ","snp4.10:14.3":"Dhammesu ca na gacchati, ","snp4.10:14.4":"Sa ve santoti vuccati”ti. ","snp4.10:14.5":"Purabhedasuttam dasamam. "}